import styled from "styled-components"

const Container = styled.div``
const Navlogo = styled.span``
const NavItems = styled.div``
const Button = styled.button``

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
    <Navlogo>
    <NavItems>
    redoxBooking
    <Button>click</Button>
    <Button>click</Button>
    </NavItems>
    </Navlogo>
      
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Navbar
